{"tid":2330871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"許智峯：銀行戶口被凍結後 信用卡亦被停用！","createTime":"2020-12-18T10:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T01:36:00.000Z","uid":22556,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"75e97cdbe3fa750b8909e3e4380cfdd31272b26c","tid":2330871,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"許智峯表示，宣佈流亡後隨即發現自己及家人的銀行戶口被凍結，連信用卡都無法進行交易，而有關信用卡的資料也在網上銀行戶口「消失」（Vanished），令他無法在當地銀行提取金錢。對於警方指控他涉嫌挪用眾籌款項，他直斥警方此舉是出於政治報復（political retaliation），目的旨在損害他的個人聲譽、令港人對他失去信心。許認為，政權有意向所有擁有銀行戶口的港人散播白色恐怖，令他們懼怕自己的資產會突被凍結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159704087757448/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10159704087757448%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=2682fabd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10159704087757448/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"70a7b08a929724d9dc714353f638a7f286af6ed7","tid":2330871,"uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:40:45.000Z","msg":"李大導又立下大功"},{"pid":"b8d64e43d0f08da64c1fdee375bd0046711e4e14","tid":2330871,"uid":77196,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:40:51.000Z","msg":"班狗小心嚇多兩嚇成邨人衝去DRAW CASH呀，怕你一時間冇咁多CASH引起恐慌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6644af807c116ded03a31e3341d918bd4a2cbe","tid":2330871,"uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國製金融中心"},{"pid":"45c619e53fcbf01bde6f9b60485364f752547c0c","tid":2330871,"uid":57397,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T10:49:34.000Z","msg":"咁仲使唔使交卡數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97080897c0c9cbc3e68a11a35f415727f3a05d6","tid":2330871,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco